latestIgtvVideos.title: Best Dessert!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This is Chocolate explosion.
Well the dessert is humongous and can cater 6 people together at a time. 
It’s mixture of delicious macaroons icecream, caramel popcorn, different types of chocolates and brownies, topped with candy floss and liquid nitrogen.
It’s one of the most amazing, drooling and mind blowing dessert in Mumbai; India.

Step into the world of L’Atelier 1664 as it makes its grand debut in India.

A French lifestyle brand that embodies the art of refined living, L’Atelier 1664 seamlessly blends luxury, fashion, design, and gastronomy to create unforgettable experiences.

L’Atelier 1664 India unveiled its Studio Experience at Lakmé Fashion Week, a curated journey designed to celebrate the essence of creativity and elegance.

Follow @latelier1664india for a taste of effortless sophistication.

What if the space around you could fuel your ambition? 
What if it could push you to do more, move more, and be more? 

That’s the feeling I got at Hiranandani Westgate in Hiranandani Estate, Thane. A place designed not just for comfort, but for progress. Where one can work with focus, play with passion, and recharge with ease. 

Because a great life isn’t just about where you live—it’s about how you live. 
And here, everything is designed to inspire living excellence.
